Title: Work Log 2
Text:
@realAbbowser: Hey, you! Have you finished it?
@recruitZ: At the current pace, we should be able to finish the work on schedule. However, some of the given materials are missing, such as Cube snacks and cakes.
@realAbbowser: H-how could they be missing?
@recruitZ: Everything was complete when I took inventory. Someone might have been stealing a bite. We can check the surveillance video.
@realAbbowser: No! Don't check the videos! If they're missing, they're missing. Sort this out yourself!
@recruitZ: Okay.
